###
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/auth/me/password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "oldPassword": "matkhau_moi_123", 
  "newPassword": "12345678"
}

###
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/auth/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "password": "matkhau_moi_123"
}

### Cập nhật profile có kèm ảnh
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

Huy Xai Postman
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="tải xuống.jpg"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./tải xuống.jpg
--WebAppBoundary--